ga therapy section to learn which yogic practices have been shown.";i:40;s:174:"Chair seated twist pose benefits the following muscles and hence can be included in yoga sequences with the corresponding muscles focus 5 Steps to Master Revolved Chair Pose.";i:41;s:58:"Twisted Chair Pose strengthens and stretches calf muscles.";i:42;s:42:"Opens your shoulders chest and upper back.";i:43;s:55:"Revolved chair Pose improves the motion in your ankles.";i:44;s:48:"Stimulates your abdominal organs and your heart.";i:45;s:122:"This pose is not for those who are suffering from insomnia low blood pressure headache or those with ankle or knee injury.";i:46;s:33:"Pregnant women dont attempt this.";i:47;s:74:"Revolved Chair Pose is a detoxifying little deeper standing-twisting pose.";i:48;s:187:"Twisting the body by keeping the palms together into a prayer position while balancing the lower body with legs bent in knees kept together challenges the physical and mental flexibility.";i:49;s:33:"Revolved Chair Pose Instructions.";i:50;s:70:"Start in mountain pose and as you exhale bend your knees and sit back.";i:51;s:109:"Twist your torso to the right place your left elbow on your right knee and turn your gaze toward the ceiling.";i:52;s:48:"Stay in revolved chair pose for 30 seconds to 1.";i:53;s:71:"A universal twisting pose that is done while you are seated on a chair.";i:54;s:70:"The chair in this case acts as a prop that helps you deepen the twist.";i:55;s:74:"So this pose has several variations depending on how you sit on the chair.";i:56;s:64:"One of the variations involves you facing the back of the chair.";i:57;s:72:"Begin in chair pose with knees together and weight mostly in your heels.";i:58;s:77:"Bring your hands together into a prayer position at the center of your chest.";i:59;s:30:"Inhale to lengthen your spine.";i:60;s:98:"Exhale to hinge forward then twist to your right hooking your left elbow outside your right thigh.";i:61;s:72:"Press your palms together to create